Steven Universe is one of the best cartoons on the Cartoon NETWORK channel on HBO max and hulu and warner bros. We love Steven, Pearl, Garnet, Ameythst, Connie, Lars, Sadie, Peridot, Lapis Lazuli, Aquamarine, White Diamond, Pink Diamond, Rose Quartz, Greg Universe, Ronaldo and all the other characters in anime series. It is weird and wacky but wholesome and fun. So today on Spilling The Milk we react to Rebecca Sugar's masterpiece television series the roundtable, cartoon universe, theories, lars, sadie, gem fusion, homeworld
